===Etymology===
Probably a {{calque|en|fr|courbe de Bézier|nocap=1}}. {{named-after|en|occ=Renault engineer|Pierre Bézier|wplink==}} who popularized the curves developed earlier by {{w|Paul de Casteljau}} and used them to design curves for the bodywork of cars.

